** Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar (YaMCATS) - Meeting 31
** Monday 19th June, 2023
** School of Mathematics, University of Manchester

The 31st meeting of the Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar (YaMCATS) will be held at the University of Leeds on Monday 19th June. The speakers will be

Adrian Miranda (University of Manchester)
Chiara Sarti (University of Cambridge)
Markus Szymik (University of Sheffield)
A message was moved here from #seminar: YAMCaTS > 2022 December 15 meeting by Nicola Gambino.
